---
title: Peanut-Hoisin Chicken Tenders Stir-Fry with Bok Choy and Peppers
description: Feeling nutty today? This stir-fry combines bold hoisin, zesty Moo Shu Spice Blend and earthy peanut butter to make a savoury sauce that coats juicy chicken tenders, served with tender-crisp bok choy, sweet bell peppers and buttery basmati rice.
